{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 324.243,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.158,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, having been born of good parents,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.338,
      "end": 7.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I was taught somewhat in all the learning of my father;",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.326,
      "end": 10.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and having seen many hardships in the course of my days,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 11.082,
      "end": 14.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but, having been highly favored of the Lord in all my days;",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 14.838,
      "end": 19.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, having had a great knowledge of the goodness and the mysteries of God,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 19.244,
      "end": 22.588,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I make a record of my proceedings in my days.",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 23.268,
      "end": 26.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, I make a record in the language of my father,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 26.977,
      "end": 29.949,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which consists of the learning of the Jews",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 30.129,
      "end": 32.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the language of the Egyptians.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 33.363,
      "end": 36.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I know that the record which I make is true;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 36.422,
      "end": 38.465,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I make it with my own hand;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 38.645,
      "end": 40.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I make it according to my knowledge.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 41.554,
      "end": 44.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For then in the beginning of the first year",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 44.428,
      "end": 47.354,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of the reign of Zedekiah, king of Judah,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 47.534,
      "end": 51.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "(my father, Lehi, having dwelt at Jerusalem in all his days);",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 51.801,
      "end": 54.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in that same year there came many prophets,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 55.139,
      "end": 56.904,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prophesying to the people",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 57.084,
      "end": 58.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they must repent,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 58.797,
      "end": 61.816,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or the great city Jerusalem must be destroyed.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 62.496,
      "end": 65.004,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And so my father, Lehi, as he went forth",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 65.184,
      "end": 66.531,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prayed to the Lord,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 66.711,
      "end": 69.451,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even with all his heart,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 69.631,
      "end": 71.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in behalf of his people.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 71.797,
      "end": 73.84,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then as he prayed to the Lord,",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 74.02,
      "end": 75.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there came a pillar of fire",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 75.965,
      "end": 78.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and dwelt upon a rock before him;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 78.56,
      "end": 80.696,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he saw and heard much;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 80.876,
      "end": 84.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and because of the things which he saw and heard",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 84.214,
      "end": 86.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he quaked and tremble greatly.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 86.937,
      "end": 90.234,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then he returned to his own house at Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 90.414,
      "end": 92.643,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he cast himself upon his bed,",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 92.823,
      "end": 94.913,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "being overcome with the Spirit",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 95.093,
      "end": 97.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the things which he had seen.",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 97.956,
      "end": 100.51,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And being thus overcome with the Spirit,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 100.69,
      "end": 103.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was carried away in a vision,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 103.192,
      "end": 105.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that he saw the heavens open",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 105.74,
      "end": 108.805,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he thought he saw God sitting upon his throne,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 108.985,
      "end": 111.864,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "surrounded with numberless crowds of angels",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 112.044,
      "end": 115.388,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the attitude of singing and praising their God.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 116.068,
      "end": 117.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then he saw One",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 117.734,
      "end": 120.428,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "descending out of the middle of heaven,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 120.608,
      "end": 122.558,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he saw that his brightness",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 122.738,
      "end": 125.199,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was above that of the sun at noon-day.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 125.879,
      "end": 128.433,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also saw twelve others following him,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 128.613,
      "end": 132.096,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their brightness exceeded that of the stars in the sky.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 132.776,
      "end": 134.494,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they came down",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 134.674,
      "end": 137.321,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and went forth upon the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 137.501,
      "end": 139.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the first came",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 139.26,
      "end": 141.118,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and stood before my father,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 141.298,
      "end": 143.109,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and gave to him a book,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 143.289,
      "end": 145.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and told him that he should read.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 145.919,
      "end": 147.684,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then as he read,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 147.864,
      "end": 150.186,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was filled with the Spirit of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 150.866,
      "end": 152.445,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he read, saying:",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 152.625,
      "end": 154.297,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Woe, woe, to Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 154.477,
      "end": 156.892,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have seen your wicked practices!",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 157.072,
      "end": 161.391,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, and many things did my father read concerning Jerusalem\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 161.571,
      "end": 163.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it should be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 163.516,
      "end": 165.374,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the inhabitants of it;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 165.554,
      "end": 167.83,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many should perish by the sword,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 168.01,
      "end": 171.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and many should be carried away captive into Babylon.",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 171.941,
      "end": 174.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then when my father had read and seen",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 174.629,
      "end": 176.858,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many great and marvelous things,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 177.038,
      "end": 179.685,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he exclaimed many things to the Lord; such as:",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 179.865,
      "end": 182.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Great and marvelous are your works,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 182.413,
      "end": 184.085,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord God Almighty!",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 184.265,
      "end": 186.448,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Your throne is high in the heavens,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 186.628,
      "end": 187.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and your power,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 188.062,
      "end": 189.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and goodness,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 189.403,
      "end": 190.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and mercy",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 190.79,
      "end": 193.391,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are over all the inhabitants of the earth;",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 193.571,
      "end": 195.614,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and, because you are merciful,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 195.794,
      "end": 199.602,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you will not suffer those who come to you that they shall perish!",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 200.282,
      "end": 203.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner was the language of my father",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 203.527,
      "end": 205.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the praising of his God;",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 205.657,
      "end": 207.19,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for his soul rejoiced,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 207.37,
      "end": 209.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his whole heart was filled,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 209.593,
      "end": 211.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the things which he had seen,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 212.049,
      "end": 214.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, which the Lord had shown to him.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 215.005,
      "end": 220.392,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, do not make a full account of the things which my father has written,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 220.572,
      "end": 222.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he has written many things",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 222.981,
      "end": 225.489,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he saw in visions and in dreams;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 225.669,
      "end": 228.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he also has written many things",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 228.217,
      "end": 231.05,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he prophesied and spoke to his children,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 231.23,
      "end": 233.552,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which I shall not make a full record.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 234.232,
      "end": 237.483,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But I shall make a record of my proceedings in my days.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 237.663,
      "end": 241.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I make a summary of the record of my father,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 241.419,
      "end": 244.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon plates which I have made with my own hands;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 244.943,
      "end": 248.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, after I have summarized the record of my father",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 248.885,
      "end": 251.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then will I make a record of my own life.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 251.933,
      "end": 254.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, I would that you should know",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 254.389,
      "end": 258.847,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after the Lord had shown so many marvelous things to my father, Lehi,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 259.027,
      "end": 262.417,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, concerning the destruction of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 262.597,
      "end": 264.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold he went forth among the people,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 264.96,
      "end": 266.678,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and began to prophesy",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 266.858,
      "end": 271.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to declare to them concerning the things which he had both seen and heard.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 271.903,
      "end": 273.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the Jews mocked him",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 273.848,
      "end": 277.006,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the things which he testified of them;",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 277.186,
      "end": 282.341,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he truly testified of their wickedness and their wicked practices;",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 282.521,
      "end": 286.376,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he testified that the things which he saw and heard,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 286.556,
      "end": 289.435,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the things which he read in the book,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 289.615,
      "end": 292.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "manifested plainly of the coming of a Messiah,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 292.999,
      "end": 295.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the redemption of the world.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 295.862,
      "end": 299.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when the Jews heard these things they were angry with him;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 299.943,
      "end": 302.637,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even as with the prophets of old,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 302.817,
      "end": 304.628,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whom they had cast out,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 304.808,
      "end": 306.526,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and stoned, and killed;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 306.706,
      "end": 308.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they also sought his life,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 308.79,
      "end": 310.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might take it away.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 112
